    "featuredImage": "https://s3.me-central-1.amazonaws.com/files.prestigeone.ae/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/10115046/WhatsApp-Image-2025-04-10-at-11.49.41_cfb0e188.jpg",
    "excerpt": "Dubai, UAE – April 2, 2025 – Prestige One Developments has officially appointed AE7 as the full design consultant for its upcoming 45-storey mega waterfront development in Dubai. The collaboration brings together Prestige One’s expertise in high-end real estate with AE7’s extensive experience in architectural design, e",
    "contentHtml": "Dubai, UAE – April 2, 2025 – Prestige One Developments has officially appointed AE7 as the full design consultant for its upcoming 45-storey mega waterfront development in Dubai. The collaboration brings together Prestige One’s expertise in high-end real estate with AE7’s extensive experience in architectural design, engineering, and master planning. AE7 is a globally recognized firm with a portfolio that includes large-scale commercial, residential, and mixed-use developments across the Middle East, North America, and Europe. The firm specializes in creating integrated, functional spaces that align with the evolving demands of modern urban environments. Their involvement in this project will contribute to the development of a waterfront destination that fully leverages the site’s unique potential, blending visionary design with practical functionality. Commenting on the partnership, Mr. Ajmal Saifi, CEO of Prestige One, said: “Waterfront developments have the potential to transform a landscape, and this project is focused on bringing something truly unique to Dubai’s real estate market. AE7’s global expertise, combined with Prestige One’s international reach, will bring that vision to life, setting new standards on a global scale.” The agreement marks the start of the planning and design phase, with AE7 leading the architectural and engineering aspects of the project. Prestige One Developments continues to expand its portfolio with projects that emphasize high end living and prime locations. The appointment of AE7 reflects its approach to working with industry leaders to deliver developments that align with Dubai’s 2040 vision. Further details about the project will be shared as the development progresses.",
